己開槍就屈人搶槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b2f94736ea0ac425fd3dda03e2c99d93dc43e2","tid":1710706,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e755f084932c7bcd82386d768753b004988b33e","tid":1710706,"uid":152976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T08:34:22.000Z","msg":"鳩解法例收收皮喇屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:33:00.000Z","msg":"公安條例寫明私人地方要手令<br />\n<br />\n佢咁講咁條條例應該係廢<br />\n廢左佢就仲好"}]}